latestPosts.caption:
I have no idea who I think I am at this point…

Maybe the 15 years styling & watching models on set has paid off, maybe not! Either way I had a great time @pose.photostudio 

The camera is hidden in the mirror and you get an hours shoot alone in the studio with a few props and a speaker for your playlist 🙌🏼 

It would be great for a family shoot, with your friends, for a special occasion or for headshots. Honestly, I wasn’t sure whether to do it when they got in touch but I’m so glad I did! If you want to try it you can get 15% off with the code CAROLINE15 

Let me know if you do! And be kind 🙈

*pr app

They come with a matching top which is great too but I love to separate co-ords & hang them as individual items in my wardrobe to get more wear out of them. You know I’ll be wearing the top with jeans too.

latestPosts.caption:
Do you double denim?

If you love a co-ord and the ease of getting dressed when you’re wearing one, make your own with any denim in your wardrobe.

No hard and fast rules really just play with shapes and silhouettes. I prefer my denim to loosely match in tone but it doesn’t have to be perfect, don’t overthink it, just give it a go. A tee or vest will help break it up if it’s feeling a lot!

I’ve linked what I’m wearing with sizing details on my @ltk.europe 

Jeans @arketofficial 
Shirt @sezane 
Best @uniqlo 
Trainers @golaclassics
